org.gbif.common.messaging.api.messages

Class StartCrawlMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.common.messaging.api.messages.StartCrawlMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message, DatasetBasedMessage

    public class StartCrawlMessage
extends Object
implements DatasetBasedMessage
    Message to send to request a new crawl of a dataset.

    A priority can be given to this request. Lower numbers mean higher priority. Requests with a higher priority will be running first but there is no guarantee on the scheduling algorithm so consider this as a hint.
